Figure 7: Possible theoretical framework for the LMI - adding both ban-rate and ladder win-rate, using three main subdimension: ban, playrate and strength



Having the LMI as seen in Fig:8. The ban-rates shows a stronger causal relationship with the win-rates compared to the playrates (Fig:4) so considering it part of the strenght of a deck can be considered more appropriate. This the option which tries to follows the definition which was given before: ‘The performance of a deck is defined by its own strength and popularity inside the metagame.’ and is in fact the framework which is proposed.



